(8, 'Community Energy Conservation & Smart Monitoring Seminar', 'Community energy conservation focuses on reducing overall energy consumption through collective efforts such as using energy efficient appliances, promoting renewable energy sources, and encouraging behavioral changes like switching off unused devices. When paired with smart monitoring systems often powered by IoT technology communities can track real-time energy usage, detect wastage, and optimize consumption patterns. These systems provide data-driven insights, enabling households, schools, and public facilities to make informed decisions, lower costs, and reduce carbon footprints. Together, conservation practices and smart monitoring create a sustainable, efficient, and environmentally responsible community energy model.', 'Energy Efficiency Division', 'Facility Admin', '09123456789', 'lcristianmarkangelo@gmail.com', '2026-01-30', '13:00:00', '16:30:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'public', 'orientation', 'small', 1, 'no', 1, 0, 0, NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'approved', NULL, '{\"facility\":{\"facility_id\":18,\"facility_name\":\"QC M.I.C.E. Auditorium\",\"facility_capacity\":300},\"scheduled_date\":\"2026-02-28\",\"scheduled_start_time\":\"13:00\",\"scheduled_end_time\":\"16:00\",\"assigned_equipment\":\"Extension Cord (50 meters), LED Projector + Screen Package, Monobloc Chair (White), PA System (Premium), Wireless Microphone (Additional)\",\"approved_budget\":\"29299.00\",\"budget_breakdown\":{\"food\":[{\"name\":\"Mega Meal \\u2013 Chicken McDo w Fries & McFlurry\",\"qty\":100,\"unit_cost\":228,\"subtotal\":22800}],\"materials\":[{\"name\":\"Workbook\",\"qty\":100,\"unit_cost\":64.99,\"subtotal\":6498.999999999999}],\"other\":[{\"name\":\"Certificate\",\"qty\":100,\"unit_cost\":0,\"subtotal\":0}]},\"admin_notes\":null,\"approved_at\":\"2026-02-14 13:38:41\",\"approved_by\":\"Admin\"}', 83, 3124, 4, '2026-02-14 05:31:20', '2026-02-14 05:38:41'),
